tps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Shirley-Manson-and-Iggy-Pop-696x441.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Shirley-Manson-and-Iggy-Pop-1392x882.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Shirley-Manson-and-Iggy-Pop-1068x677.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2004px) 100vw, 2004px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/iggy-pop">伊基·波普 (Iggy Pop)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shirley-manson">雪莉·曼森 (Shirley Manson</a> ) 等人将出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/marianne-faithfull">玛丽安·费斯福尔 (Marianne Faithfull)</a>翻唱的新专辑中。</p><p>在唱片中，Iggy 与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cat-power">Cat Power</a>翻唱了 Faithfull 的《Working Class Hero》，而 Manson 则与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/peaches">Peaches</a>合唱了《Why D&#39;Ya Do It》。</p><p> 《The Faithful: A Tribute to Marianne Faithfull》将于 12 月 8 日发行，收录了众多艺术家翻唱的 Faithfull 歌曲（请参阅下面的完整曲目列表）。</p><p>该唱片的所有利润将直接用于帮助 Faithfull 从长期的新<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marianne-faithfull-says-she-almost-died-after-battling-covid-19-2857753" target="_blank" rel="noopener">冠肺炎</a>中恢复过来。您可以<a href="https://www.intheqrecords.com/products/the-faithful-a-tribute-to-marianne-faithfull" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订唱片。</p><p> Parkington Sisters 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-breeders">The Breeders</a>的 Tanya Donelly 现在分享了她们对 Faithfull 歌曲“This Little Bird”的演绎，您可以在下面收听。</p><p> “从童年到今天，玛丽安的声音一直是我最喜欢的乐器之一，她的音乐和精神一直是我一生的灵感，”唐纳利在一份声明中说。</p><p> “I wanted to cover &#39;This Little Bird&#39; for its fragile and beautiful musical arrangement and melody, and the bittersweet story the lyrics tell. A total honor to get to sing and play this lullaby, and The Parkington Sisters elevate with their vocal and string magic. We&#39;re so grateful to be able to pay tribute to this amazing singer/songwriter and woman.” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Tanya Donelly &amp; the Parkington Sisters - This Little Bird (Marianne Faithfull Tribute)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/49nJeAA1rwM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <strong>&#39;The Faithful: A Tribute to Marianne Faithfull&#39; Tracklist is:</strong><em><br /><strong><br /></strong></em> <strong>Disc 1</strong><br /> <strong>01. Tracy Bonham – &#39;As Tears Go By&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>02. Tanya Donelly &amp; The Parkington Sisters – &#39;This Little Bird&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>03. Josie Cotton – &#39;Summer Nights&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>04. Sylvia Black – &#39;Sister Morphine&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>05. Cat Power &amp; Iggy Pop – &#39;Working Class Hero&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>06. Shirley Manson &amp; Peaches – &#39;Why D&#39;Ya Do It&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>07. Pom Poms – &#39;Brain Drain&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>08. Bush Tetras – &#39;Guilt&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>09. Joan as Policewoman – &#39;Broken English&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>10. Tammy Faye Starlite &amp; Barry Reynolds – &#39;The Ballad Of Lucy Jordan&#39;</strong></p><p> <strong>Disc Two</strong><br /> <strong>01. Honeychild Coleman – &#39;Over Here (No Time For Justice)&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>02. Adele Bertei – &#39;Times Square&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>03. Nicole Atkins &amp; Jim Sclavunos – &#39;Strange Weather&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>04. Lydia Lunch – &#39;Love, Life, and Money&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>05. Cynthia Ross (the B Girls) &amp; Tim Bovaconti – &#39;Vagabond Ways&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>06. Donita Sparks – &#39;Sliding Through Life on Charm&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>07. Miss Guy – &#39;Sex With Strangers&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>08. FaithNYC – &#39;Kissin&#39; Time&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>09. Feminine Aggression – &#39;Before The Poison&#39;</strong></p><p> Back in 2021, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marianne-faithfull-doesnt-know-if-shell-sing-again-after-covid-19-battle-2929675">Faithfull said that her near-fatal battle with coronavirus almost robbed her of the ability to sing.</a></p><p> The 73-year-old artist <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marianne-faithfull-is-being-treated-in-hospital-for-covid-19-coronavirus-2641097">was hospitalised in March 2020 after developing coronavirus symptoms</a> . After 22 days of treatment, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marianne-faithful-has-left-hospital-after-covid-19-treatment-2651842">she was discharged from hospital</a> and returned to her London home in April.</p><p> “The damage has been very bad,” she told the <em><a href="https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/music/story/2021-04-27/marianne-faithfull-courtney-love-poetry-cheating-death-sober-sex?fbclid=IwAR0YkPAY5vRjZcenoKfwvvckpZzHq_wuZIm0nt0b3WCYs38iGkZEHVXHm9o" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LA Times</a></em> in 2021 <em>.</em> “It&#39;s my lungs, my memory and fatigue. It couldn&#39;t be worse. I don&#39;t know if I will ever be able to sing again. I have singing practice once a week, and I&#39;m doing my best, but it&#39;s very hard.”</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iggy-pop-shirley-manson-and-more-to-appear-on-marianne-faithfull-covers-album-3536472">Iggy Pop, Shirley Manson and more to appear on Marianne Faithfull covers album</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
